AmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1ejq154nqzo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1ejq154nqzo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Erik%20Menendez%20denied%20parole%20three%20decades%20after%20killing%20his%20parents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755830218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Ffe29%2Flive%2F7cfe6290-7eb2-11f0-a5e2-236e16f99597.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3wnlldjp20o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20younger%20of%20the%20Menendez%20brothers%2C%20who%20killed%20their%20parents%20in%20their%20Beverly%20Hills%20mansion%2C%20can%20try%20again%20for%20parole%20in%20three%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3wnlldjp20o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3wnlldjp20o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3wnlldjp20o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%202%20Gurugram%20Teens%20Diverted%20250%20Kilos%20of%20Plastic%20Waste%20Into%20Everyday%20Products%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20sit%20around%20waiting%20for%20some%20stitching%20work%20to%20come.%20Weeks%20would%20pass%2C%20and%20there%20would%20be%20nothing.%20My%20students%20would%20ask%20if%20they%20should%20look%20for%20work%20elsewhere%2C%20and%20at%20home%2C%20I%20often%20had%20to%20borrow%20money%20to%20buy%20food.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20sustain%20as%20there%20was%20no%20stability%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neelam%2C%20a%20sewing%20instructor%20at%20Sahaj%20Shakti%20Foundation%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20provides%20vocational%20training%20and%20livelihood%20support%20to%20women%20from%20low-income%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20her%20routine%20at%20the%20Sahaj%20Shakti%20Foundation%20in%20Gurugram%20was%20marked%20by%20frustration%20and%20uncertainty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20sewing%20instructor%2C%20she%20dedicated%20her%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288638%2Fkashmiri-women-earn-from-crewel-embroidery-initiative-zamruda-bano%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20young%20women%20basic%20embroidery%20and%20hand-stitching%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20hoping%20to%20empower%20them%20with%20a%20means%20to%20earn%20a%20livelihood.%20However%2C%20work%20was%20scarce%20and%20opportunities%20few.%20The%20lack%20of%20steady%20work%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20her%2C%20and%20the%20women%20she%20guided%20often%20found%20themselves%20waiting%20days%20for%20even%20a%20small%20stitching%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20scene%20is%20different.%20Neelam%20and%20nearly%2050%20women%20from%20the%20Sahaj%20Shakti%20Foundation%20are%20engaged%20in%20creating%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%2C%20including%20laptop%20sleeves%2C%20tote%20bags%2C%20wallets%2C%20folders%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20improvement%20worth%20noticing%20is%20the%20material%20they%20work%20with%2C%20which%20is%20discarded%20PVC%20(polyvinyl%20chloride)%20flex%20banners.%20These%20banners%2C%20once%20strung%20up%20across%20streets%20advertising%20everything%20from%20school%20functions%20and%20political%20rallies%20to%20festive%20melas%2C%20were%20typically%20thrown%20away%20after%20brief%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20often%20end%20up%20clogging%20drains%20or%20littering%20empty%20plots%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20growing%20plastic%20waste%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20two%20teenagers%20took%20the%20lead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20began%20with%20two%20teenagers%20from%20Gurugram%2C%20Samvit%20Govindani%2C%20aged%2016%2C%20and%20Shaurya%20Sharma%2C%2017.%20Both%20are%20students%20at%20Delhi%20Public%20School%20International%20(DPS)%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20and%20they%20are%20the%20founders%20of%20%E2%80%98Project%20ReFlex%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20aiming%20to%20repurpose%20discarded%20banners%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346052%2Findian-startups-turning-waste-into-eco-friendly-products-trash-to-treasure-watch-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epractical%20and%20stylish%20everyday%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-21T191825.199_11zon-1755784129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98Project%20ReFlex%E2%80%99%20is%20an%20initiative%20aiming%20to%20repurpose%20discarded%20banners%20into%20stylish%20everyday%20products%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-21T191825.199_11zon-1755784129.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-21T191825.199_11zon-1755784129-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-21T191825.199_11zon-1755784129-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-21T191825.199_11zon-1755784129-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-21T