.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-05-21-at-10.03.16-AM_11zon-1755672875.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D489352%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20thoughtful%20ramps%20to%20respectful%20staff%2C%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Birsa%20Munda%20Hockey%20Stadium%20shows%20what%20true%20accessibility%20can%20look%20like%2C%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20passionate%20hockey%20fan%20Manpreet%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F489352%2Fbirsa-munda-accessible-stadium-wheelchair-user-story-manpreet%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranchi%20Teacher%20Transforms%20Roadside%20Garbage%20Spot%20into%20a%20200-Plant%20Garden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManoj%20Ranjan%2C%20a%20teacher%20by%20profession%2C%20has%20turned%20the%20roadside%20space%20outside%20his%20home%20in%20Ranchi%E2%80%99s%20Harmu%20housing%20colony%20into%20a%20thriving%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20a%20place%20with%20limited%20space%2C%20he%20found%20his%20passion%20for%20gardening%20constrained.%20However%2C%20his%20resolve%20led%20him%20to%20utilise%20the%20small%20patch%20outside%20his%20home%20%E2%80%93%20once%20a%20dumping%20ground%20for%20garbage%20%E2%80%93%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20my%20village%2C%20I%20used%20to%20plant%20many%20trees%20along%20with%20my%20father.%20But%20when%20my%20family%20moved%20to%20Ranchi%20for%20work%2C%20there%20was%20not%20much%20space%20in%20the%20new%20house%20to%20plant%20trees.%20I%20noticed%20how%20people%20would%20throw%20garbage%20outside%20our%20house.%20So%2C%20we%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20garden.%20Today%2C%20this%20spot%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20place%20for%20passersby%20to%20stop%20and%20take%20selfies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%2C%20Manoj%20has%20pursued%