0grains%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20nutrition%20they%20carry%20%E2%80%94%20back%20into%20local%20diets.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20solution%20or%20resilience-building%20effort%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20meet%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20these%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pranay%20Karuna%2C%20Associate%20Director%20at%20Dasra%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20philanthropic%20foundation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20protecting%20indigenous%20knowledge%2C%20native%20seeds%2C%20and%20natural%20resources.%20From%20planning%20to%20execution%2C%20the%20work%20must%20consider%20all%20the%20different%20challenges%20these%20communities%20face.%20By%20focusing%20on%20farming%20and%20building%20local%20resilience%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20connects%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20with%20social%20inequalities%20and%20shows%20why%20solutions%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20local%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dasra%2C%20this%20approach%20is%20not%20new.%20Over%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20the%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%20co-founded%20by%20Neera%20Nundy%20and%20Deval%20Sanghavi%20%E2%80%94%20has%20directed%20more%20than%20%24420%20million%20toward%20social%20causes%2C%20supported%20over%201%2C400%20nonprofits%2C%20and%20positively%20impacted%20approximately%20200%20million%20lives.%20One%20of%20its%20most%20effective%20strategies%20has%20been%20to%20build%20alliances%20with%20like-minded%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%2010to19%20Alliance%2C%20which%20empowers%20adolescents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20positive%20life%20choices%2C%20to%20%E2%80%98Youth%20Ke%20Bol%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20building%20a%20coalition%20of%20one%20million%20young%20people%20for%20better%20access%20to%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20services%2C%20to%20the%20National%20Faecal%20Sludge%20and%20Septage%20Management%20(NFSSM)%20Alliance%2C%20which%20works%20with%20governments%20and%20municipalities%20on%20liquid%20waste%20%E2