ground%20visits%2C%20giving%20all%20stakeholders%20a%20clearer%20picture%20of%20how%20these%20services%20are%20managed%20day%20to%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOpening%20doors%20to%20new%20frontiers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Saahas%2C%20the%20CRA%20opened%20doors%20that%20had%20long%20been%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%20Tripathi%20says%20they%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20the%20Northeast%20but%20struggled%20to%20secure%20funding%20or%20a%20practical%20entry%20point.%20%E2%80%9CAbout%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20started%20work%20in%20Assam%20through%20some%20other%20funding.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20active%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20locations%20in%20the%20state.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20CRA%2C%20we%20can%20scale%20our%20work%20in%20more%20cities%20because%20alliance%20partners%20have%20come%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Saahas%20operates%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Jorhat%20and%20Majuli.%20With%20Janaagraha%20taking%20the%20lead%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20been%20proactive%20in%20its%20support.%20%E2%80%9COn%20our%20own%2C%20we%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20clout%20to%20talk%20to%20state%20authorities%20and%20convince%20them%20to%20back%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Archana%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%20has%20helped%20us%20find%20our%20footing%20in%20Assam.%20Now%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20also%20on%20the%20technical%20committee%20in%20Lakhimpur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20for%20solid%20waste%20management.%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20CRA%20partners%20work%20in%20urban%20spaces.%20%E2%80%98Farmers%20for%20Forests%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Pune-based%20nonprofit%2C%20focuses%20on%20protecting%20and%20restoring%20forest%20cover%20in%20close%20collaboration%20with%20rural%20communities.%20Co-founder%20Krutika%20Ravishankar%20says%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20challenges%20has%20been%20sustaining%20collaboration%20with%20governments%20%E2%